<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> The evoker is a 12th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 15, +7 to hit with spell attacks). The evoker has the following wizard spells prepared:</p>

<p>Cantrips (at will): fire bolt<em>, light</em>, prestidigitation, ray of frost*</p>

<p>1st level (4 slots): burning hands<em>, mage armor, magic missile</em></p>

