<p>3rd level (3 slots): counterspell, fireball<em>, lightning bolt</em></p>

<p>4th level (3 slots): ice storm*, stoneskin</p>

<p>5th level (2 slots): Bigbyâ€™s hand<em>, cone of cold</em></p>

